headline: WARNER BROS. DISCOVERY PRESIDENT OF INTERNATIONAL, GERHARD ZEILER TO PRESENT AT THE UBS GLOBAL MEDIA AND COMMUNICATIONS CONFERENCE
summary: Warner Bros. Discovery, Inc. (Nasdaq: WBD) today announced that Gerhard Zeiler, President, International, will present at UBS' Global Media and Communications Conference on Tuesday, December 10, 2024 at 12:00 p.m. ET.
